ce with Ushahidi v2. Share your experiences with us. </span><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1kNWUXVfJs8KGj0LSbIGZ9UiC_Wr8PFlXJsnHJ2Lm4N0/edit#heading=h.koyyn2qxwob1" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Instructions here</span></a></p></li><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1IbIE2c_08t1j_PWg32A05lkPAo7AWY59R40Cgcdqf98/edit#heading=h.n9fhyp2b7g3" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Disaster response</span></a></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1Frd2RveoCBJR_G0uwlt9wpKXigg1RhF5PeqqxoX3J2M/edit" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Human Rights Mapping</span></a></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/document/d/1sD5b-DZUgCMhVCensP26XjvG1hGwT2s3YlbHgUHL-PM/edit" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Anti-Corruption Mapping</span></a></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:Arial;color:r